    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly and the car handles well on the road, making it a dependable choice for any buyer. While the exterior and interior are generally clean, you may find some minor cosmetic imperfections consistent with regular use, such as small stone chips or light seat wear. Overall, it is a solid, reliable vehicle that is ready for many more miles.",
