      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold as-is, ideally for parts or as a major restoration project. The engine requires significant repairs to be reliable, and there are noticeable leaks throughout the drivetrain. Visually, the exterior suffers from widespread rust, peeling clear coat, and several large dents, while the interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. Prospective buyers should expect to invest substantial time and capital into mechanical and cosmetic overhauls.",
