      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a vehicle of uncompromising caliber. This specimen has been maintained to an exacting standard, preserved in showroom condition both mechanically and aesthetically. With its flawless finish and pristine interior, it represents the pinnacle of its class. An exceptional acquisition for the discerning driver who demands nothing less than perfection.",
